Tank Fran=C3=A7aise, since this can ding and scratch the watch.<br/><br/>Th=
e Baignoire bangle was the =E2=80=9Cfirst time a watch was released for wom=
en and got the waitlist treatment,=E2=80=9D Wallner told me. Bulgari is als=
o committing to women=E2=80=99s watches, specifically mechanical ones. In 2=
022, the brand released the Serpenti Misteriosi secret watches, powered by =
the BVL 100 Piccolissimo=E2=80=94the smallest mechanical movement of the 21=
